data: .main-menu-bg-wide{height:26px;width:100%;background-color:#2A3B4D}#splash_page{position:fixed;top:0;bottom:0;z-index:999999;background-color:#fff;text-align:center;font-family:Verdana, Arial;left:0;right:0}#splash_page .logo{margin-top:13px;float:left}#splash_page .logo-container{height:71px;background-color:#fff;overflow:hidden}#splash_page .logo-center{width:98%;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;height:auto;overflow:hidden;padding:0 9px}#splash_page p{font-size:22px;margin-bottom:3px;color:#434343}#splash_page .splash-loader{position:relative;width:100%;min-height:50px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center}#splash_page .splash-loader .loader{display:inline-block;border:16px solid #ddd;border-radius:50%;border-top:16px solid #00b6ee;-webkit-animation:spin .7s linear infinite;animation:spin .7s linear infinite;height:50px;width:50px}#splash_page .splash-text{margin-top:140px;text-align:center}#splash_page .splash-text p,#splash_page .splash-text span{text-align:center}#splash_page .splash-sub-text{color:#434343;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:26px;text-align:center}@-webkit-keyframes spin{0%{-webkit-transform:rotate(0deg)}100%{-webkit-transform:rotate(360deg)}}@keyframes spin{0%{transform:rotate(0deg)}100%{transform:rotate(360deg)}}#splash_page .logo{margin-top:13px;background-image:url('../../Broker0/Default/img/_light/logo.svg');background-repeat:no-repeat;background-size:100% auto;background-position:center;height:47px;width:163px}
